940
00:47:23,110 --> 00:47:32,670
Rym: Now, most gambling in the sad loser sense tends to use point spreads and different mechanisms to pretty much always make the odds even.

941
00:47:33,451 --> 00:47:35,054
Rym: Because that's what's best for the house.

942
00:47:35,496 --> 00:47:41,430
