Scott: What are you using?

976
00:49:03,191 --> 00:49:05,195
Scott: I can totally fuck with that.

977
00:49:07,499 --> 00:49:14,130
Scott: Even if your casino was legit, the integrity of the game itself is under question because it is in software.

978
00:49:14,690 --> 00:49:26,390
Rym: But at least if it's regulated and tested, then the incentive is entirely on the house to maintain its integrity and odds because if it doesn't, people are going to win more often.

979
00:49:27,071 --> 00:49:27,893
